OL,3,CMurder charge after man killed in hit-
OL,4,Cand-run
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,7,Fafter a pedestrian died in a hit-and-
OL,8,Frun crash.
OL,10,FStefan Wheeler, 31, was due to appear
OL,11,Fat Doncaster Crown Court on Monday,
OL,12,FSouth Yorkshire Police said.
OL,14,FA 26-year-old man died after being hit
OL,15,Fby a silver Hyundai on Prince's
OL,16,FStreet, Doncaster at about 8.30pm on
OL,17,FFriday, 10 April.
