OL,6,FDet Insp Adam Watkinson said: "I am
OL,7,Fthankful for everyone who has provided
OL,8,Finformation so far, and we are still
OL,9,Fappealing for those with dashcam
OL,10,Ffootage, and witnesses to the incident
OL,11,Fto come forward."
